400 (Bad Request) HandlerUsage:return res.badRequest();return res.badRequest(data);return res.badRequest(data, 'some/specific/badRequest/view');e.g.:```return res.badRequest(  'Please choose a valid `password` (6-12 characters)',  'trial/signup');```
